OL,5,FTHE 1NT OPENING BID continued          
OL,7,G  There isn't a great case for bidding 
OL,8,F1NTGat teams or rubber bridge, but at  
OL,9, duplicate pairs it can be just as      
OL,10, damaging to miss part scores. Equally, 
OL,11, if your opponents have the balance of  
OL,12, strength it isn't a bad idea to push   
OL,13, then about a bit!                      
OL,14,   When playing duplicaate pairs not    
OL,15, vulnerable, it is increasingly common  
OL,16,Gto play theCMini No-trumpG(10-12       
OL,17, points). It is a roller coaster, giving
OL,18, plenty of excitement and lots of tops  
OL,19, and bottoms. Is your nerve up to it?   
