OL,5,FBRIDGE NEWS                            
OL,7, TheCBourne Bridge ClubGwill hold a     
OL,8, Swiss Teams event on 8th November in   
OL,9,GFarnham, Surrey. For information phone 
OL,10,GMrs J De Gaye on 01428 604145.         
OL,12, Leading player David price will visit  
OL,13, heats of theCNational Bridge Challenge 
OL,14,Gconsisting of at least 10 tables and   
OL,15,Grun one-hour workshops free of charge. 
OL,16, Bookings will be taken on a first come 
OL,17, first served basis. For further details
OL,18, ring 0181 942 9506.                    
